Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,[* full title would be awkward here]
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,

Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.99,0:00:26.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Black crow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.11,0:02:04.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We even got an apartment for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:07.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He better not turn out to be a flop once he's serialized.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:14.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:26.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:35.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how the crow feels!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:42.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Niizuma-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.81,0:02:44.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,'Sup bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.00,0:02:45.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to keep the door locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.04,0:02:47.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:49.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe how many people live here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:51.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:53.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.91,0:02:57.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you bought a sound system.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:03:00.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought it with what I had left over after giving the prize money to my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:03.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't turn it up so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:05.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of your neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:08.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That lady was staring at me outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:12.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Niizuma-kun, I'm sorry to bring this up so suddenly,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:14.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't suppose you could get a fifty-page draft ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:17.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want a draft, there's one on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:19.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your new work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.12,0:03:23.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's about four chapters there so far— how does it look?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:26.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This, even though you're already about to be published.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.73,0:03:28.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't calm down without drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:31.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I write what I come up with at school as soon as I get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:36.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:37.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your stuff is getting better and better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.70,0:03:41.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need the first page plus a spread in color.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:42.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to draw in color.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.97,0:03:44.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel somewhat confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:45.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,When's the deadline?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.86,0:03:49.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be great if you had it done by the start of March next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.47,0:03:51.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can easily get it done by sometime in January.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:53.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like you to come pick it up around that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:57.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid of Tokyo trains and crowded places.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:03:59.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I understand. Well—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:09.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't read like a shounen manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:12.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this just some desperate gamble?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:16.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't even two months left until the Next deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.20,0:04:17.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.91,0:04:21.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuujin, mind if I make the art like it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:22.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:27.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think a more dramatic style would suit {\i1}Money and Intelligence{\i0} better. {TLC/QC: For consistency, make this the romaji and the english in a TL Note?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:29.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:35.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Hattori-san didn't say anything about that, but I think you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:37.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:40.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, why have you been staring at that postcard survey?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:42.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:48.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Please enter the numbers of manga you found entertaining, in order of interest."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:49.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It always says that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:53.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are twenty-one manga to choose from, and only three slots.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:55.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes the probability of getting picked one in seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:58.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, twenty-one divided by three is seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,0:05:04.06,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori-san said that if two out of ten people select a given manga, it will become popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.39,0:05:08.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one in five people. One fifth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.94,0:05:10.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that would be easy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:15.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but getting the average from 1-to-7 to 1-to-5 is actually quite difficult, I've realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:18.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:21.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not everyone is going to submit a vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:24.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, there's no point in us calculating that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:26.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have that kind of free time, start writing names.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:29.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to turn them into clean copies, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:31.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't hand a draft with your artwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:36.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, but it's a story about buying and selling the contents of human minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:39.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The harder I think about it, the harder it gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:43.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I came up with it, it's deeper than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.97,0:05:47.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori-san told us to depict human greed realistically.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:49.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And as repulsively as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:53.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well it's about buying and selling, so shouldn't it be easy to come up with something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:59.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well if it were up to you, Saikou, for how much would you sell the contents of your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:01.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it would depend on who I'm selling it to, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:03.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten million yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:04.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:08.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it would be horrible to have someone know the inside of your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.94,0:06:12.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want to sell it to anyone I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:14.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be easier to sell to a total stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:18.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So we need a rule saying that you can only buy from the original owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:22.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be problematic for a third person to obtain them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:29.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you would sell for ten million, and buy the contents of Azuki's brain for nine million?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:31.83,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that me and Azuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:34.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, as if I would buy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:37.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want to know what's going on in the head of someone I love. {QC: Lit. "If I knew what was going on in the head of someone I liked, that would be scary.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:39.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I knew, it would wreck the romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:46.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, rather than selling to her, I might even want to pay her to take a look in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:48.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.08,0:06:51.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want her to know how much I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:59.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, I do want to take a peek in her head after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:02.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she loves me just as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:05.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We would understand each other better than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:10.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're really into mutual love and understanding, huh.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:14.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's when I told her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:16.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first highlight, so let's make this panel a little larger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.84,0:07:18.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we should work on that line a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:20.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, I'll think of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:23.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want something striking, with impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:25.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, drawing a manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:28.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Saikou, your art is so freaking awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:30.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Huh? Manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:31.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:33.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we can't concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.13,0:07:35.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:37.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:38.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:39.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something with erotic scenes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:43.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not. We're trying to get into Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:46.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack, huh? You're sure ambitious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.08,0:07:48.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us know when you get serialized.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:49.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll brag to my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:51.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as if you're the one getting published.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:55.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's being real supportive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:07:56.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Supportive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.07,0:07:59.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's called 'being a bother'.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.46,0:08:00.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:05.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Saikou. How did your mock exam go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:07.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,For Kita High, eighty percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:11.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That qualifies me for early admission, so I guess I don't have to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:12.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:14.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninety-five percent!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even score one hundred percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:19.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you go to a better school?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.61,0:08:21.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. Kita's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.84,0:08:24.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides if I changed plans all of a sudden, Miyoshi would kick my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.89,0:08:27.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you're going to Kita for Miyoshi's sake, not mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:32.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. Around Christmas, I'm going somewhere with Miyoshi to see some lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:34.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I would invite you guys along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:36.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:37.41,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:39.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki also said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:40.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:41.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,O–Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:48.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let her distract you from writing manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:49.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:12.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright everyone, take care not to catch cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:14.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:21.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Miho! Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:22.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.77,0:09:28.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.37,0:09:29.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.49,0:09:35.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After graduation, it's possible we won't be able to meet until our dream comes true.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:39.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Compared to that, winter break should be nothing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:45.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuujin, let's go to the studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:47.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I've got plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:48.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that was today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:51.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know I shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:56.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.01,0:10:05.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, did you wait long?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:06.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:07.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:08.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:11.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll be so far away from one another after graduation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:14.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it always going to be like this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:16.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though she's so close by?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:20.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:24.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I lost track of time picking out an outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:26.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y–Your clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:29.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't go to that movie at the back-to-school party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.26,0:10:32.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking about how this was our first date, I was getting super freaked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:35.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shorts in December?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:36.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I can see her midriff.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:39.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I feel like something is pressing against my arm!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:40.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, were you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:44.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and I wasn't thinking about anything weird either!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:47.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just wondering whether you were cold in that outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:48.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you freaking out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.78,0:10:49.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.16,0:10:51.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:52.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:54.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already so crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.94,0:10:58.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, there are more people here than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:02.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get separated in there, we'll never find each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:04.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we'll be fine since we have our cellphones.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:07.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we pick a meeting place just in case?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:08.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:12.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi, you're so sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.32,0:11:13.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:15.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:16.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling shy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.34,0:11:18.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:01.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get Miho and him at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.67,0:12:04.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if they're already thinking of marriage,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.94,0:12:06.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,shouldn't they be making as many memories together as they can?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:10.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I don't want it to get out, at school, that they're together...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:14.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But they aren't even sending texts! What's up with those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:20.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet Miho can say, "I love boys," without batting an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.23,0:12:26.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't let her distract you from writing manga.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:30.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki seems a bit too serious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:33.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she's crazy serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:34.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:40.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,When Saikou wrote in his notebook, "After our dream comes true, no matter what,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.68,0:12:41.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.98,0:12:47.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think they're more in love than we can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.65,0:12:50.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"More than we can imagine,"{\i0} eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:53.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not just romanticism.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:57.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If Azuki and he were to start dating now,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:13:00.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she might lose herself in him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:05.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if she cried because she wasn't sure if she could have both love and her dream.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:09.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,How miserable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.37,0:13:10.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:13.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Love is a miserable thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:17.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I understand why you're always alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:21.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, when I'm alone I can praise my own intelligence in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:26.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm going to do some names. Meeting adjourned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:27.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:35.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for, Miyoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:03.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard Azuki has an exam today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:05.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,For a school in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:06.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard that from Miyoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:07.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:09.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm switching the positions of the speech bubbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.68,0:14:10.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:13.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you care about Azuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:14.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm concentrating on this manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:16.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's doing her best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:18.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:21.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:25.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,"No! I don't want to be apart from her! I hope she fails that exam!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:26.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is what I thought you would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:28.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:31.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And what would we do if someone overheard you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:33.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I only said that because no one was around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.53,0:15:39.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Would the fourth of February work for you to go hand in the name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.49,0:15:42.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go right after the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:44.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:46.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't done anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:49.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kita High's exam questions are textbook-level, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:52.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Those should cover the main points.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:54.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:58.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not going to surprise us with really hard questions this year are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:00.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If they do, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:06.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,These were all I studied.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.93,0:16:08.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:13.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel like I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.14,0:16:15.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I sucked on that exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:17.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who takes that exam passes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:21.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, I'm not sure about you since you were suspended for that violence incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:24.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,They said it wouldn't end up on my permanent record.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:29.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And even if it does, my grades are more than good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.83,0:16:31.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll beg me to go to school there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:34.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyaa! I love that about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:36.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're as weird as him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:41.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.95,0:16:44.26,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's interesting as it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:49.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but how about adding that part from your Tezuka submission "100,000,000 Minutes," {TLc}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:53.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,about the gigantic government supercomputer that ranks people? {Timing}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:55.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:16:59.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,My uncle used to say that the best editors are the ones who come up with ideas you'd never have yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:04.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't I... I mean, why didn't I realize?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:06.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:09.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rewrite it, then bring it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:10.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:12.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for your advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:25.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:27.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you actually nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:28.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:29.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:31.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it, Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.55,0:17:35.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad, I'm so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:38.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's get back to the studio and fix up that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.54,0:17:39.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:48.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! You're good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:52.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And the art is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:54.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Going for a realistic style was the right choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.62,0:17:56.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll really push this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:18:00.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Vice Editor-in-Chief and our captain will decide which ones make it onto the pages of NEXT!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:03.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Vice Editor and captain? Not the Editor-in-Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:08.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. The Vice Editor at NEXT! needs more on-the-job experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:13.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, the final OK comes from the Editor-in-Chief, but the selection is made by those under him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.18,0:18:18.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Editor-in-Chief also has the final say when it comes to our magazine as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:23.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The results will be out in two weeks, and I'll give you a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:23.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:29.26,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize it wasn't the Editor-In-Chief who selects the work for printing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:30.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:33.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you didn't know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:33.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:37.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "If it's interesting, it will get published," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.94,0:18:38.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.26,0:18:46.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Two weeks, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:47.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Saiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:48.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.68,0:18:51.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that great, Kawasaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.61,0:18:52.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You got into high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:54.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sensei! It's all thanks to you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.72,0:18:57.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with you today? You're being awfully proper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:19:00.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm really grateful to you, sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:04.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawasaki, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:07.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Men do not show their tears to others!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:11.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,These are my last words to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:13.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the last line of this play...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:19.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I draw a title page?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:22.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it'll help us calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:29.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy Valentine's!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:32.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, thanks for making the trip even though it was your day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.66,0:19:34.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to give it to you while it's still Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:37.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, home-made!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.81,0:19:40.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry if they're not well made.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:41.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Want one, Saikou?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.12,0:19:44.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, if I steal one Miyoshi will hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:46.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:47.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.03,0:19:51.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,These are great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:54.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What about tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:54.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:57.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,These are from Miho.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.37,0:20:00.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:05.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Open it, Saikou.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.73,0:20:07.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, don't be shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.09,0:20:11.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I'll open it after I get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:26.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:29.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry these aren't handmade like Kaya's.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.19,0:20:32.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be embarrassing if my family saw me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.07,0:20:36.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I got you pencil chocolates since you're trying to become a manga artist...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:37.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,is that dumb?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.06,0:20:40.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Moritaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.27,0:20:41.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.03,0:20:43.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:21:01.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this as the last one?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:05.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:07.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.89,0:21:08.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.49,0:21:16.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That took a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.57,0:21:18.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because there was so much strong work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.97,0:21:19.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aida-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:22.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.75,0:21:24.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.73,0:21:31.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We were so confident with our Tezuka submission, but it failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.30,0:21:34.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what to expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.72,0:21:39.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:41.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, this is Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.25,0:21:43.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,They decided to run it in NEXT!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:46.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,YES!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:49.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man! This is the happiest I've ever been in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:53.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,M–Me too! This feels so much better than getting into high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.26,0:21:58.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray! Hurray! Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:21:58.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.77,0:21:59.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.97,0:22:01.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.99,0:22:04.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought this over, and I'll be honest with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.60,0:22:05.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.11,0:22:09.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're running a fifty-page work by Niizuma Eiji from the cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.64,0:22:11.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Niizuma Eiji, from the cover?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.82,0:22:13.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Part of the reason they included your work
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:16.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,was in order to make him look better, since you're the same age.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.00,0:22:21.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just using us? {There was an astrisk (*) on this line.  Nfi why.}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.62,0:22:23.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.35,0:22:27.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting your work published in NEXT!, whatever the reason, is a big opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.23,0:22:30.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please work with the intention of beating—no...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.34,0:22:31.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Win!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.24,0:22:33.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:40.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.78,0:24:17.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we snag the number one spot at NEXT! we'll get serialized!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.47,0:24:19.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that happens, go on a date with Miho!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.46,0:24:20.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to wait until after our dream comes true.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.98,0:24:22.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I so do not get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.47,0:24:25.21,Main,Next episode,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: "Feast and Graduation"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.31,0:24:27.21,Main,Next episode,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean your dream has to come true?
